    <questionvariables>
      <text><![CDATA[x0:0;
u1:2*x^2+1
k1:4;
eq1:k1*sqrt(u1)+1;
f0:ev(eq1,x=x0);
dq1:diff(eq1,x);
ta1:castext("Let
`
u={#u1#} => (du)/(dx) = {#diff(u1,x)#}
`
Hence
`
f(x) = int {#dq1#} dx
     = int 2/sqrt(u) du.
     = {#k1#} sqrt(u)+c
     = {#k1#} sqrt({#u1#})+c
`
Using the given values `5 = 4sqrt({#ev(u1,x=x0)#})+c => c=1`, we have
`
f(x) = {#eq1#}
`");
ta2:f(x)=eq1;]]></text>
